data.description: Welcome to this newly constructed home, just 2 years young! Featuring 4 generously sized bedrooms, a loft and 2nd floor laundry. Open concept connects living, dining and kitchen areas, ideal for entertaining or just everyday activities. Also includes oversized kitchen island for additional seating and countertop space. Spacious backyard on a premium wooded lot provides ample privacy.  Home is perfectly located near I75 for easy commute to Dayton or Cincinnati.  Close proximity to an abundance of shopping and dining options. Beautiful developing neighborhood features 2 playgrounds, ponds, dog park, side walks and more! Come check out this home and all it has to offer in highly sought after Sawyer's Mill Community!
